Sanlam Says Headline Earnings Increased Up to 35% in Six Months to June 30

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-16T07:01:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-16/sanlam-says-headline-earnings-increased-up-to-35-in-six-months-to-june-30.html
Sanlam Ltd. (SLM)  said headline earnings
per share for the six months to June 30 are expected to rise
between 25 percent and 35 percent from a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
